{"type": "article", "id": 24378, "title": "有印章的香皂包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-24T07:00:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 77, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607164817XIDjgdPT1W0eNFoK.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个香皂包装最明显的特征是上面的蜡印，常用于信封封口而像一个小的浮雕，立刻让包装拥有古典的优雅。蜡印盖在纸壳和一层很薄的木料之间，木料上用印刷体居中写下了相应的文字，给人一种阅读的感觉，也体现出这款香皂的精致和贵重。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164814AMKmxXYs5dDfecTg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164814ZuIsCvrmXdgk8wih.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164815MyQa8Yo1sB4ibqlJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071648155YfbTMNwQ6Ji3BHZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071648159x4muSlVhnEJFDtw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51092896\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}